Dialogue: 9,0:00:06.01,0:00:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Không biết nữa...{I don't know.}
Dialogue: 9,0:00:06.97,0:00:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nếu là giao báo thì cũng quá sớm.{It's too early to be a newspaper salesman.}
Dialogue: 9,0:00:11.30,0:00:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Xin lỗi.{Salutations!}
Dialogue: 9,0:00:12.74,0:00:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Xin lỗi?{Salutations?}
Dialogue: 9,0:00:13.75,0:00:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma Vương đại nhân,\N hình như là...{My lord, could it be...}
Dialogue: 9,0:00:23.31,0:00:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Là cô gái "té cầu thang" ngày hôm qua à?{That girl who fell down the stairs yesterday?}
Dialogue: 9,0:00:25.09,0:00:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hình như là thế.{Probably.}
Dialogue: 9,0:00:27.30,0:00:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Xin lỗi!{Salutations!}
Dialogue: 9,0:00:28.88,0:00:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,V-Vâng?{y-yeah?}
Dialogue: 9,0:00:31.13,0:00:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Xin lỗi vì quấy rầy gia đình vào sáng sớm.{I'm sorry to trouble you at this hour.}
Dialogue: 9,0:00:33.31,0:00:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tôi tên là Kamazuki Suzuno, từ nay sẽ sống ở căn hộ kế bên.{My name is Kamazuki Suzuno. I have taken residence in the dwelling abreast your own.}
